Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.95,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tower of Law"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Tower of Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin realized that Luffy and\Nthe others had come to rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That's not what we agreed upon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return for my cooperation, you were\Nsupposed to let them escape safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They came here after leaving\NWater Seven safely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're hopeless scum. They don't\Nhave a shred of morality in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, we don't even have to\Nkeep our promises with you criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Take this! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so cocky, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dirty coward...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The receiver is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take Cutty Flam to Impel Down\Nand Nico Robin to Navy Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the escort ship is ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll go through the\NGates of Justice and sail off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go back to your rooms\Nand take it easy for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What dependable guys my subordinates are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have them, I feel like I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, urging the King Bull\Non in pursuit of Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:29.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Courthouse" "Main Island Front Gate"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats were moving\Nforward without a hitch, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get on without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are going smoothly! Good thing\Nwe've got you guys on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you to\Nget us to Luffy, King Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's asking, "By the way, was it\Nokay that the guy with the mask
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't get on with you guys?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Hm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:03:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I-I can't find Sogeking anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.99,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Courthouse" "Main Island Front Gate"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lieutenant Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find him! Find Straw Hat at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for Luffy, he finally reached\Nthe rooftop of the courthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the last building.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air Door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You're that bull guy\Nwho was with the pigeon guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did think that there was no way\Nthere'd be only five casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, that was a big surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the start of the World\NGovernment, it's unprecedented...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for a man to step this far\Ninto the Government's entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you planning to keep fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get running, get running,\Nholding our flag high in the sky{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's cross this endless sea to go in search of{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a global miracle no one\Nhas yet been able to find{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With our hearts pounding,\Nwe'll just charge ahead as we please{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}following the footprints of\Nthose who chase their dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how stormy the night,\Nif we join our hearts as one,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we will be able to make it through{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get running, get running,\Nholding our flag high in the sky{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though there are tears\Nwe don't want anyone to see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chase it, chase it,\Nif we want to achieve our dream,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we should always look\Nstraight ahead without fear{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can't stop here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Around the world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Start me up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get running, get running,\Nhead past everyone else{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So long as we don't run from it,\Nwe can grasp tomorrow in our hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chase it, chase it,\Neverything we see before us,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}let's carve it into the blank pages of our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brand New World{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Start me up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Give Robin Back! Luffy vs. Blueno!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Wh-Wh-What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we don't have the option\Nof going back to get him at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll work things out on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are guards everywhere on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't Luffy. If he's by\Nhimself, his life will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surmounting each island,\Nwe got stronger without knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He, too, always survived\Nlife-or-death situations on each island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one in our group would die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Always"? "In our group"?!\NWhat're you talking about, Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking came here to help us rescue\NRobin because Usopp asked him to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is an invincible hero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking is a super hero\Nfor justice. He'll definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.98,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Main Island Front Gate"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed to get on the King Bull...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do? I'm way behind now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battleship Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, those shipwrights are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I left the group. Shall I just run?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No! Running is the last thing I'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Usopp! I'm a man! I went so far\Nas to hide my identity to follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're facing a crisis where Robin is\Nsacrificing herself to protect all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right... There's only\None way to get to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry out "Operation Disguise Myself\Nas One of the Government Personnel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Pass by Them Unnoticed"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that'd be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What?! What?!\NAre they trying to drown me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy attack! Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How regrettable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! The giant woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We screwed up in our 50th year!\NI'm sorry, bosses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bosses?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are a disgrace to Elbaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Elbaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elbaf... Bosses...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...! I-Is it possible that\Nyou're from Elbaf, that warriors' village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I am Sogeking from the island of snipers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you explain to me what\Nyou're talking about in detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a total stranger from God knows where!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! Warriors from Elbaf\Nare the proudest men in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you're crying a river here.\NIt must be a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use in telling you about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Kashii were pirates\Nup until 100 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we ran amok all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--But one day on some island...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each one of 'em bagged an\Ninsanely huge Sea King, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're Elbaf giants,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nobody can take down those jumbo-sized\Nbeasts except for our bosses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those ones were definitely the biggest ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! The biggest ones we've ever caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So which one was bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Which...\N--...one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is slightly bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish! Mine's a whole\Nthree centimeters bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bosses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two bosses started a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a battle in which they put their\Npride on the line. It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the signal for the duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The group was split up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone ended up\Ngoing back to their hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The central mountain... That's Little Garden...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a life-or-death battle between warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, the winner was\Nsupposed to come back to the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but even after several decades,\Nneither of them came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After 50 years passed, me and Kashii\Nthought something was wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we set out to sea to go get those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on our way, we got caught by the Navy\Nand they made us tell them everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, in return, we were told a shocking story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that our bosses,\Nwho were very strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were confined in the government's large prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--That was about 50 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government presented conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If me and Kashii worked for\Nthe Government for 100 years--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in other words, if we could protect this\Ngate in Enies Lobby for 100 years--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'd release our bosses\Nand let us all go home to Elbaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since a giant's life span is 300 years,\Nwe thought 100 years was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we accepted the conditions and\Nhave kept fighting for the past 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the gate was broken open today by pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think something like this happened...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Our bosses will now be\Nimprisoned for the rest of their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! H-H-Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something funny about that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing funny about it!\NIf you're gonna laugh at our pride, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I didn't mean it that way!\NI meant that it's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because during our journey before\Nwe came here, we met those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two you're talking about,\Nthe Elbaf warriors Dorry and Broggy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have been fighting an evenly matched duel\Non that island for the past 100 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How come you know their names?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That can't be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna hear more proof,\NI'll tell you as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't believe me?! What do I\Nhave to tell you to get you to believe me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About their weapons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their techniques?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,73,466 duels...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,73,466 draws...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really met them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:15:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fought desperately to protect our pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, no matter what\Nmanner of enemy there may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we will not let them\Ndestroy your pride, friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in us, and continue straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight ahead! Straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already been eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight ahead! Straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakoku Sovereignty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're flying out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They cut... the very sea itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the strength of Elbaf warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore to myself to look\Nup to them as my masters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become a man of great\Npride like them some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you don't believe me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big fat lie that they\Ngot caught 50 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our bosses are alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I'm relieved... I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:52.57,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Main Island Front Gate"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.82,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Courthouse"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! We're almost to the courthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring them down without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! King Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We brought down one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! I have to treat him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodom! Stand firm! Don't fall yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Move over right away! Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodom can't go on much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His pectoral muscle got hurt by a trench mortar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move over now before he falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's gonna be saved\Nunless you guys move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "Go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's riding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Robin is in that building behind you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way, bull guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you guys haven't noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that what you're doing is a world-class crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get to the point already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government is a\Nhuge, powerful organization
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that counts more than 170 countries\Naround the world as its members.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Invading this island,\Nwhich is under its possession,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is an act of revolt against all those countries!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon their dignity, the Government\Nwill expose all of you to public ridicule
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and bestow a merciless death upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are only a few dozen people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is nowhere near enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was tell you to get out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My point is that you who entered the gates\Nof Enies Lobby already have no future,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether I move out of\Nyour way or not. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting is a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you got a good taste of our\NSix Powers at Galley-La's mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as well as the difference in\Nour levels of fighting ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason, I don't feel\Nlike I'm gonna lose at all now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I don't remember him\Nbeing as powerful as he is now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I fought him at the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world this, the Government that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just came here to get Robin back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We fight harder against\Nthe wall that confronts us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We charge ahead stronger\Nwith overflowing power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't fear even if we\Nhave to give up everything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because it's all to ensure we smile in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll become No. 1{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll aim for freedom in wonderland{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look, there's a faint light\Nshowing us the road to tomorrow,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}an era created by risking everything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.73,0:22:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We always try our best, let's go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we want to achieve glory,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}now is the time--don't be afraid{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll surely win the future\Ntogether with friends{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, we start running faster\Ntowards the vast world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can take off with unknown powers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We don't fear, and we don't waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what happens,\Nin the end we'll surely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We fight harder against\Nthe wall that confronts us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We charge ahead stronger\Nwith overflowing power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:23:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't fear even if we\Nhave to give up everything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Charge ahead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's start running towards tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because it's all to ensure we smile in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. Enemies are gathering\Nfrom the front and the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.30,0:23:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! There're thousands of enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get surrounded in a place\Nlike this, we can't move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,0:23:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--What's the matter, Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomorrah... Gomorrah's saying something!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't Stop! Hoist the Counterattack Signal!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
